===Etymology===
{{L.}} ''[[congressus]]'', from ''[[congredi]]'', past participle ''-gressus'', to go or come together; [[con-]] + [[grati]] to go or step, ''[[gradus]]'' step

===Noun===
'''congress'''
#The collective body of senators and representatives of the people of a nation.
#A gathering or assembly; a conference.

